{"tid":2245241,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"寶琳站包圍休班站長 何梓聰及營業員被裁定非法集結罪成","createTime":"2020-10-16T05:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T07:10:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"b7a58db504400e6527985d3524375e34028e1694","tid":2245241,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:28:13.000Z","msg":"學生和營業員去年9月4日參與包圍港鐵寶琳站，期間包圍調景嶺站休班站長要求交「831封站」原因，兩人今在觀塘法院被裁定非法集結罪成。<br />\n<br />\n兩名被告依次為22歲學生何梓聰(曾為西貢區環保北選區候選人)及23歲被告，兩人同被控於去年9月4日，在港鐵寶琳站內，聯同其他人參與非法集結。<br />\n<br />\nsource: 頭條"},{"pid":"565f961effcdb47dc9578f5cdf5077ce7f9151da","tid":2245241,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:32:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10365\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10365&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=2335da11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10365</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">還押候判<br />\n詳情後補</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d95753377f6591ac465c57501c49d686d235b52a","tid":2245241,"uid":204539,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:34:35.000Z","msg":"隻光頭狗人扯人口罩唔算襲擊？"},{"pid":"dadedc0b26d485e6bd64c5d6d95bc4a31003ea6d","tid":2245241,"uid":68553,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:34:42.000Z","msg":"2條友非法集結？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90118e0211985a2fdb5885d121fff787dae74a4a","tid":2245241,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dadedc0b26d485e6bd64c5d6d95bc4a31003ea6d","tid":2245241,"uid":68553,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:34:42.000Z","msg":"2條友非法集結？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:35:44.000Z","msg":"聯同其他人"},{"pid":"0fa47caa8b6c3a2889e941f29bd62eebf170ea97","tid":2245241,"uid":